{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_01","textHome":"再次自我介绍，我是环彩羽。@平时在官方宣传漫画「魔法☆报告」里，@和小圆前辈一起为大家传达魔法纪录的情报！@这次以4星的身份登场了！是4星哦！@难得出场，请为了抽到我而努力吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":401}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_17","textHome":"可以带3个记忆结晶了……@嗯，真难选……@虽然小圆前辈的记忆也不错……@但还是这个吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_18","textHome":"记忆结晶换好了！@话说，那边绑着两条缎带的粉毛是谁？@颜色跟我重了吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":201}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_19","textHome":"感谢你在我身上使用了贵重的素材！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_20","textHome":"我要顶替小圆前辈进支援栏了，因为是4星！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_21","textHome":"因为作为4星实装了，@这段声音应该可以在档案功能里听到。@来自魔法报告的我是4星！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_22","textHome":"终于……终于！心心念念的5星！@感谢培养我到现在！@今后也请多指教5星的我……@小圆前辈说……@「目前的情况充满了死亡flag的气息」……@别、别说这种话啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"id":120100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":120100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":401}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1201_00_23","textHome":"你好，我是越过了小圆前辈立起的@死亡flag，成为了6星的环彩羽！@这6颗星真是耀眼啊。就从这些星星里，@放出把敌人一扫而空的光束……@我大概做不到，不过小圆前辈的话……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":120100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":120100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp